As per the latest report from Dubai Tourism & Economy Department, Dubai welcomed about 8.1 million international visitors in the first seven months of 2022.

Dubai received 7.12M international overnight guests in the first half of 2022 an increase of 183% compared the same period of time in 2021. The increase is due to opening post-COVID and revitalisation of various industries within the country and region.
